  The following video modes are added:<br />
  <code>
    1024x800, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1280x720, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1280x800, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1360x768, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1366x768, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1400x1050, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1440x900, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1600x800, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1680x1050, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1920x1080, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1920x1200, 60Hz refresh<br />
    2048x1080, 60Hz refresh
  </code>
</p>
<h2>Ultra-HD resolutions</h2>
<p>
  Adds several Quad-HD and UHD resolutions to the list of available modes.  <strong>Your GPU must support 4096 wide textures for these modes to work.</strong><br />
  The following video modes are added:<br />
  <code>
    2560x1080, 60Hz refresh<br />
    2560x1440, 60Hz refresh<br />
    2560x1600, 60Hz refresh<br />
    2560x1920, 60Hz refresh<br />
    2560x2048, 60Hz refresh<br />
    2800x2100, 60Hz refresh<br />
    3200x1800, 60Hz refresh<br />
    3200x2048, 60Hz refresh<br />
    3840x2160, 60Hz refresh<br />
    3840x2400, 60Hz refresh<br />
    4096x2304, 60Hz refresh<br />
    4096x3072, 60Hz refresh
  </code>
</p>
