<h1>Common SVGA resolutions</h1>
<p>
  Adds several common 4:3 and 5:4 display resolutions used by SVGA type graphics adapters.  This option is useful when running under Wine on a system that doesn&#8217;t support mode switching.<br />
  The following video modes are added:<br />
  <code>
    640x480, 60Hz refresh<br />
    800x600, 56Hz refresh<br />
    800x600, 60Hz refresh<br />
    1024x768, 60Hz refresh<br />
